Cherrypick RNAi Clones by Keyword

Cherrypick RNAi Clones by Keyword

cherrypick(identifier, format = "keyword")

Arguments

identifier

Keyword identifier.
format

Identifier format.

Value

RNAi clone list by gene.

Examples

cherrypick("unfolded protein response", format = "keyword") %>%
    glimpse()
#> Observations: 62
